<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[sorantak의 기술 블로그🐾]]></title><description><![CDATA[개발 경험 위주로 작성한 글들을 모았습니다]]></description><link>https://sorantak.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2022 04:25:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[utterances로 블로그에 댓글기능 추가하기]]></title><description><![CDATA[Install 댓글기능을 추가할 블로그는 이미 만들어졌으며 Github “public” repository로 관리되고 있는 상태를 전제로 한다. Github에 로그인한 상태로 아래 링크에 들어가 앱을 다운받는다. utterances Utterances…]]></description><link>https://sorantak.github.io/etc/add_comments_to_my_blog_with_utterances/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://sorantak.github.io/etc/add_comments_to_my_blog_with_utterances/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2022 11:08:33 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2 id=&quot;install&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#install&quot; aria-label=&quot;install permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Install&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;댓글기능을 추가할 블로그는 이미 만들어졌으며 Github &lt;strong&gt;“public”&lt;/strong&gt; repository로 관리되고 있는 상태를 전제로 한다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Github에 로그인한 상태로 아래 링크에 들어가 앱을 다운받는다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apps/utterances&quot;&gt;utterances&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;utterances-composition&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#utterances-composition&quot; aria-label=&quot;utterances composition permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Utterances Composition&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;댓글기능 추가하고 싶은 레포를 선택하고 설치 버튼을 누른다.
&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 567px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 139.66666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;install_utterances&quot;
        title=&quot;install_utterances&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/044c460bf9fc7b429db2750019342ade/8710b/install_utterances.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/044c460bf9fc7b429db2750019342ade/5a46d/install_utterances.png 300w,
/static/044c460bf9fc7b429db2750019342ade/8710b/install_utterances.png 567w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;utterances는 포스트의 url, pathname, title 등등을 추적해서 git issue 기반으로 동작하기 때문에 이 중에 하나를 선택한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;나는 pathname으로..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;label, theme 등 옵션 선택을 완료하면 페이지 하단에 나의 선택을 반영한 스크립트가 완성된다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 683px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 43.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;utterances_script&quot;
        title=&quot;utterances_script&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/d2934ae14fa8ac6a76247c07d1dad8b8/bca35/utterances_script.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/d2934ae14fa8ac6a76247c07d1dad8b8/5a46d/utterances_script.png 300w,
/static/d2934ae14fa8ac6a76247c07d1dad8b8/0a47e/utterances_script.png 600w,
/static/d2934ae14fa8ac6a76247c07d1dad8b8/bca35/utterances_script.png 683w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;blog-setting&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#blog-setting&quot; aria-label=&quot;blog setting permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Blog Setting&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;5&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;위 스크립트를 복사하여 블로그 소스에 추가하면 된다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;만약, 나와 같이 블로그가 React 기반이라면 컴포넌트를 추가해야 한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;난 Jbee님의 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee&quot;&gt;템플릿&lt;/a&gt;을 사용했더니 컴포넌트는 이미 추가되어 있음 (크👍👍👍)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-jsx&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token literal-property property&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;token literal-property property&quot;&gt;utterances&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;sorantak/sorantak.github.io&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-meta-config.js&lt;/code&gt; 파일의 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;comment.utterances&lt;/code&gt;의 주석을 풀고 본인의 Github 사용자명과 블로그 레포지토리 주소만 적으면 댓글 영역이 생긴다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;finish&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#finish&quot; aria-label=&quot;finish permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Finish&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 634px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;comments&quot;
        title=&quot;comments&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/9e37387a7ad7ec2fc70ec0d1fadd022e/374ac/comments.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/9e37387a7ad7ec2fc70ec0d1fadd022e/5a46d/comments.png 300w,
/static/9e37387a7ad7ec2fc70ec0d1fadd022e/0a47e/comments.png 600w,
/static/9e37387a7ad7ec2fc70ec0d1fadd022e/374ac/comments.png 634w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TA-DA🥳&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Gatsby + Github Pages로 나만의 블로그 만들기]]></title><description><![CDATA[Install   URL SHELL git https://gitforwindows.org/  node.js https://nodejs.org/en/  gatsby   gh-pages   node.js 버전 확인 gatsby 참조 -g…]]></description><link>https://sorantak.github.io/etc/make_my_own_blog_with_gatsby_github_pages/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://sorantak.github.io/etc/make_my_own_blog_with_gatsby_github_pages/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2022 16:08:05 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2 id=&quot;install&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#install&quot; aria-label=&quot;install permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Install&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/badge/Windows-0078D6?style=flat-square&amp;amp;logo=Windows&amp;amp;logoColor=white&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;URL&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;SHELL&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;git&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://gitforwindows.org/&quot;&gt;https://gitforwindows.org/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;node.js&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nodejs.org/en/&quot;&gt;https://nodejs.org/en/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;gatsby&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;npm install -g gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;gh-pages&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;npm i gh-pages --save-dev&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;node.js 버전 확인&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;node&lt;/span&gt; --version&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;gatsby 참조&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-g 옵션은 패키지를 전역에서 참조할 수 있게 함&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;설치되면 다음 경로에서 확인 가능&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;C:\Users\{username}\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;create-project&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#create-project&quot; aria-label=&quot;create project permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Create Project&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt; 템플릿 사용&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;gatsby new &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;projectname&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Github 레포지토리 생성 후 업로드&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;run&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#run&quot; aria-label=&quot;run permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Run&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;projectname&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
gatsby develop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8000/&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8000/&lt;/a&gt; 접속하여 변경사항 확인&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;✅ 배포는 Github Pages를 사용한다 (Netlify 사용 안 함)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#build&quot; aria-label=&quot;build permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Build&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; run build

&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# 오류날 경우&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; --legacy-peer-deps

&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# 그래도 오류날 경우 package-lock.json 파일 및 node_modules 경로 하위 모두 삭제 후 다시 빌드&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;빌드를 마치면 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;/public&lt;/code&gt; 경로에 정적 파일들이 생성된다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;deploy&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#deploy&quot; aria-label=&quot;deploy permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Deploy&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;package.json&lt;/code&gt; 파일에 해당 내용 추가&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;deploy&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;gatsby build &amp;amp;&amp;amp; gh-pages -d public -b gh-pages&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; run deploy&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;위 명령어를 실행하면 package.json에 입력한 두 줄의 코드가 실행된다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;gh-pages 명령어의 -d는 /public 경로 하위의 모든 내용을 publish 함을 의미하고 -b는 push할 원격저장소의 브랜치를 의미한다 (gh-pages 브랜치가 default이며 변경 가능하다)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;작업이 완료되면 로그 마지막 줄에 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Published&lt;/code&gt; 라고 뜬다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;실제로 Github 원격 gh-pages 브랜치에 가면 빌드된 정적 파일들이 업로드된 것을 확인할 수 있다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(위와 같은 원리는 원격 gh-pages 브랜치에 push될 때 Github Actions가 동작하기 때문인 것 같다 왠지 gh-pages 라이브러리가 알아서 해주는 것 같음)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💡 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npmjs.com/package/gh-pages&quot;&gt;https://www.npmjs.com/package/gh-pages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 30.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;github_actions&quot;
        title=&quot;github_actions&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/655cb33e59619a78e8294f222cd63768/c1b63/github_actions.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/655cb33e59619a78e8294f222cd63768/5a46d/github_actions.png 300w,
/static/655cb33e59619a78e8294f222cd63768/0a47e/github_actions.png 600w,
/static/655cb33e59619a78e8294f222cd63768/c1b63/github_actions.png 1200w,
/static/655cb33e59619a78e8294f222cd63768/c65fa/github_actions.png 1434w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🌌 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;{username}.github.io&lt;/code&gt; 도메인 사용하기&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;레포지토리 &gt; Settings &gt; Pages 메뉴에 Github가 무료로 제공하는 도메인 설정이 되어 있다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;기본적으로는 Source가 master 브랜치의 루트경로로 설정되어 있어서 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;readme.md&lt;/code&gt; 파일을 보여주는 것이다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;브랜치를 gh-pages로 변경, 경로는 그대로 루트경로로 설정하면 해당 도메인으로 접속 시 올려놓은 public 하위의 정적 페이지들이 보이는 것을 확인할 수 있다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ref. &lt;a href=&quot;https://dailyco.tech/share/gatsby-blog-deploy/&quot;&gt;https://dailyco.tech/share/gatsby-blog-deploy/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🤔 궁금한 것은.. 로컬에서 작업을 끝내고 gh-pages 명령어를 사용하면 프로덕션까지 배포가 되는건데.. (through Github Actions)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그럼 마스터 브랜치에 남아있는 변경사항은 로컬에만 계속 남겨놔야 하는 것인지&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;관리를 위하여 포스트에 맞춰 커밋을 해놔야 하는건가&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;how-to-post&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#how-to-post&quot; aria-label=&quot;how to post permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;How to Post&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -D gatsby-post-gen

&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# 다음과 같은 오류 발생할 경우&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# npm ERR! code ERESOLVE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# npm ERR! ERESOLVE could not resolve&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -D gatsby-post-gen --save --legacy-peer-deps&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;package.json&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;create&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;gatsby-post-gen&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; run post
&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;# 또는&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; run create&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;다음과 같은 형식을 갖춘 새 md 파일이 생성됨&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-markdown&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token front-matter-block&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;---&lt;/span&gt;
